name: Mahna Gwee
description:
A lonely building stands in the deepwood. The sun’s light is obscured by the dense canopy. Lonely Kiel ambles towards the dilapidated home. What will they find inside?

Programming by The Iron Shark

iron-shark.itch.io

Music by Alyx Jones

https://alyxjones.itch.io/

SFX by Kevin Davey

kev-davey83.itch.io

(Unfortunately the current build doesn't really feature any gameplay! Check back in the future for some awesome puzzles and story! In the meantime enjoy the awesome witchy musical theme!)
